summary: Unpopular Opinion: I love Dan, but his generic tweets with tired jokes do nothing for me. I find myself rolling my eyes every...
body: Unpopular Opinion: I love Dan, but his generic tweets with tired jokes do nothing for me. I find myself rolling my eyes every time. I would rather him just stay gone and enjoy whatever he’s doing during his break until he’s ready to come back (or tweet genuinely interesting or funny things less frequently) than tweeting something random from the depths of his drafts once a week just to show us that he’s still alive.
